Special episodes
Special episodes which include new footage in addition to selections from previously broadcast episodes. Availability of special episodes depends on the broadcast market and language.
Special Edition (2014)
Ancient Aliens: Special Edition features highlights from previously broadcast episodes. The episodes include extended interviews with guests and some new effects. The episodes were originally broadcast as part of Season 8.
